  "narrative": "### Node n1919: Procedure `CheckClaim`\n\nThis procedure references symbols derived from its semantic block and symbol table.\n\n- **Files / DB Contracts**:\n  - HSGPSPF (columns: GPS000 CHAR, GPS010 CHAR, GPS020 CHAR, GPS025 CHAR, GPS030 DECIMAL, GPS035 DECIMAL, GPS040 CHAR, GPS050 CHAR, GPS060 DECIMAL, GPS070 DECIMAL, GPS080 CHAR, GPS090 CHAR, GPS100 DECIMAL, GPS110 DECIMAL, GPS120 DECIMAL, GPS130 CHAR, GPS140 DECIMAL, GPS150 DECIMAL, GPS160 CHAR, GPS161 CHAR +10 more)\n\n- **Variables**:\n  - 3011 (type: t.klist.3011)\n  - G73000 (type: t.char.3)\n  - G73050 (type: t.char.8)\n  - G73060 (type: t.char.2)\n  - counter (type: t.dec1_0)\n  - error\n\n- **Raw sem JSON**:\n```json\n{\n  \"sym.file.HSGPSPF\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.file.HSGPSPF\"\n  },\n  \"sym.var.G73000\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.var.G73000\"\n  },\n  \"sym.var.G73050\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.var.G73050\"\n  },\n  \"sym.var.G73060\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.var.G73060\"\n  },\n  \"sym.var.counter\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.var.counter\"\n  },\n  \"sym.var.error\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.var.error\"\n  },\n  \"sym.var.3011\": {\n    \"refersTo\": \"sym.var.3011\"\n  }\n}\n```",
  "rpgSnippet": "     P CheckClaim      B\n     D CheckClaim      PI              N\n     D*----------------------------------------------------------------\n     D counter         S              1  0 Inz(0)\n     D error           S               N   Inz(*Off)\n     D*****************************************************************\n      /free\n       errorT = *Blanks;\n       If %Trim(G73360) = '3' And G73280 = *Blanks;\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:(counter - 1) * 70 + 1:70) = 'Ursache Kampagne aber ' +\n                 'keine Kampagnen-Nr. eingetragen.';\n          G73360 = *Blanks;\n          Update HSG73LR1;\n       EndIf;\n       If G73360 = *Blanks;\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:(counter - 1) * 70 + 1:70) = 'Schadenscodierung Kund' +\n                 'e ung�ltig.';\n       EndIf;\n       If %Trim(G73360) = '3' And (G73370 <> *Blanks Or G73380 <> *Blanks);\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:(counter - 1) * 70 + 1:70) = 'Schadenscodierung Kund' +\n                 'e ung�ltig.';\n       EndIf;\n       If G73390 = *Blanks;\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:(counter - 1) * 70 + 1:70) = 'Schadenscodierung Werk' +\n                 'statt ung�ltig.';\n       EndIf;\n       If %Trim(G73390) = '97' And (G73400 <> *Blanks Or G73410 <> *Blanks);\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:(counter - 1) * 70 + 1:70) = 'Schadenscodierung Werk' +\n                 'statt ung�ltig.';\n       EndIf;\n       If G73070 = *Blanks;\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errort:(counter - 1) * 70 + 1:70) = 'Es ist keine schadens'+\n                 'verursachende Teilenummer angegeben.';\n       EndIf;\n       SetlL (G73000:G73050:G73060) HSGPSPF;\n       ReadE(N) (G73000:G73050:G73060) HSGPSPF;\n       Dow Not %Eof(HSGPSPF) And Not error;\n          If GPS040 = 'SMA' And (GPS220 = *Blanks Or GPS240 = *Blanks);\n             error = *On;\n          EndIf;\n          ReadE(N) (G73000:G73050:G73060) HSGPSPF;\n       EndDo;\n       If error;\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:counter * 1:60) = 'Es sind Sonderkosten '+\n                 'ohne Codierung vorhanden.';\n       EndIf;\n       If getClaimValues('Requested':G73000:G73050:G73060:G73065) = 0;\n          counter += 1;\n          %Subst(errorT:counter * 1:60) = 'Antrag mit Wert 0 kan'+\n                 'n nicht versendet werden.';\n       EndIf;\n\n       If counter > 0 And errorT <> *Blanks;\n          ExFmt HS1210WE;\n          Return *Off;\n       EndIf;\n       Return *On;\n      /end-free\n     P                 E",
